OL,3,CHealth board announces palliative care
OL,4,Cchanges after 'staffing challenges'
OL,6,FSpecialist palliative care has
OL,7,Fofficially been paused at a hospital
OL,8,Fin Rhondda Cynon Taf after what the
OL,9,Fhealth board describes as "significant
OL,10,Fmedical staffing challenges".
OL,12,FCwm Taf Morgannwg University Health
OL,13,FBoard has confirmed that ward six at
OL,14,FYsbyty Cwm Cynon, Mountain Ash, has
OL,15,Fformally been changed from a
OL,16,Fspecialist palliative care ward to one
OL,17,Fwhich can provide end-of-life and
OL,18,Fgeneral healthcare.
