OL,3,CHealth board announces palliative care
OL,4,Cchanges after 'staffing challenges'
OL,6,FThe health board said the ward - which
OL,7,Fwas historically consultant-led - had
OL,8,Fnot operated as a specialist
OL,9,Fpalliative care unit since January
OL,10,F2024 due to "significant medical
OL,11,Fstaffing challenges", and said
OL,12,F"providing specialist palliative care
OL,13,Fon a site without the appropriate
OL,14,Fsenior clinical expertise would not be
OL,15,Fsafe or in the best interests of
OL,16,Fpatients".
OL,18,FMore than 2,000 people have since
OL,19,Fsigned an online petition urging the
OL,20,Fhealth board to reconsider its
OL,21,Fdecision.
