OL,3,CHealth board announces palliative care
OL,4,Cchanges after 'staffing challenges'
OL,6,FThe ward had eight specialist
OL,7,Fpalliative care beds, while the
OL,8,Fcapacity for specialised palliative
OL,9,Fcare across sites in Merthyr Tydfil,
OL,10,FLlantrisant and Bridgend is 16 beds.
OL,12,FA health board spokesperson said:
OL,13,F"Providing specialist palliative care
OL,14,Fin Prince Charles Hospital, Y Bwthyn
OL,15,Fat Royal Glamorgan Hospital, and Y
OL,16,FBwthyn Newydd at Princess of Wales
OL,17,FHospital means these small number of
OL,18,Fpatients will receive the best
OL,19,Fpossible care, from the right teams,
OL,20,Fin the right place."
