OL,3,CHealth board announces palliative care
OL,4,Cchanges after 'staffing challenges'
OL,6,FHealth board statement in full
OL,8,FDom Hurford, executive medical
OL,9,Fdirector at the health board, said:
OL,10,F"We continue to provide end-of-life
OL,11,Fcare at Ysbyty Cwm Cynon. The change
OL,12,Frelates to specialist palliative care,
OL,13,Fwhich supports people with very
OL,14,Fcomplex, life-limiting conditions, not
OL,15,Fonly at the very end of life, but
OL,16,Fthroughout the course of an illness to
OL,17,Fmanage symptoms and control pain.
