OL,6,F"Only a very small number of people
OL,7,Frequire this specialist care, with the
OL,8,Fmajority needing general end of life
OL,9,Fsupport at home or in general
OL,10,Fcommunity hospital beds, including at
OL,11,FYsbyty Cwm Cynon.
