OL,3,CHealth board announces palliative care
OL,4,Cchanges after 'staffing challenges'
OL,6,F"Specialist palliative care is
OL,7,Fconsultant-led, which means expert
OL,8,Fdoctors oversee the care of these
OL,9,Fpatients. As a result of significant
OL,10,Fmedical staffing challenges, ward 6 at
OL,11,FYsbyty Cwm Cynon has not operated as a
OL,12,Fspecialist palliative care unit since
OL,13,FJanuary 2024, with patients instead
OL,14,Freceiving their care at Prince Charles
OL,15,FHospital and Y Bwthyn, at the Royal
OL,16,FGlamorgan Hospital.
