OL,3,CHealth board announces palliative care
OL,4,Cchanges after 'staffing challenges'
OL,6,F"Providing specialist palliative care
OL,7,Fon a site without the appropriate
OL,8,Fsenior clinical expertise would not be
OL,9,Fsafe or in the best interests of
OL,10,Fpatients. Whilst we understand that
OL,11,Fsome people are concerned about this
OL,12,Fchange, we will not compromise on the
OL,13,Fsafety of care for our patients.
