OL,3,CHealth board announces palliative care
OL,4,Cchanges after 'staffing challenges'
OL,6,F"We listen to our patients and their
OL,7,Ffamilies, and we know that most people
OL,8,Fwant to spend their final days at home
OL,9,Fsurrounded by loved ones. Providing
OL,10,Fmore end-of-life care in the
OL,11,Fcommunity, when this is appropriate
OL,12,Fand safe, will enable us to fulfil the
OL,13,Fwishes of these patients. Likewise,
OL,14,Fproviding specialist palliative care
OL,15,Fin Prince Charles Hospital, Y Bwthyn
OL,16,Fat Royal Glamorgan Hospital, and Y
OL,17,FBwthyn Newydd at Princess of Wales
OL,18,FHospital means these small number of
OL,19,Fpatients will receive the best
OL,20,Fpossible care, from the right teams,
OL,21,Fin the right place.
